<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to UNICX</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .qr-code {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .qr-code img {
            max-width: 200px;
            border: 2px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to UNICX!</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{firstName}} {{lastName}},</h2>
        
        <p>Welcome to UNICX! We're excited to have you join our platform.</p>
        
        <p>To complete your registration and access your account, please scan the QR code below:</p>
        
        <div class="qr-code">
            <img src="{{qrCodeImage}}" alt="Registration QR Code">
        </div>
        
        <p><strong>Instructions:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Open your mobile device's camera</li>
            <li>Point it at the QR code above</li>
            <li>Follow the prompts to complete your registration</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>This QR code will expire in {{expiryHours}} hours, so please complete your registration soon.</p>
        
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        The UNICX Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This email was sent to {{email}}. If you didn't request this invitation, please ignore this email.</p>
        <p>&copy; 2024 UNICX. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
